summary: Just something I needed to get off my chest
title: Just something I needed to get off my chest
body:
as I have been seeing this around I just wanted to say that I hope as the aggretsuko fanbase keeps going I hope the main thing people don’t think about Tadano looking back is these communist comments made about him. now I am not saying anything about it one way or the other about communism because I am not remotely political and have zero interest being one, and I don’t know if Tadano’s ideals aline with it or not I just don’t want that to be the only thing people think about when it comes to Tadano (also because its a controversial thing as well) 

I hope people see his other traits whether good or bad and see he just someone who wants to help the world

Sorry if this bothers anyone I just needed to say this
